title: 197: Grow Hard or Go Home
description: While you are building your body it is wise to build yourself as a human being. It is not always easy but how you approach it makes all the difference in the world. Sal, Adam & Justin share the struggles that have been part of their growth process. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
